1. Install ruby (and add to PATH)
2. gem install rspec cucumber webrat thistle 
3. (if on windows) 
  a. gem install win32console
  b. chcp 1252 
    (for more info: see https://rspec.lighthouseapp.com/projects/16211-cucumber/tickets/81 
      and http://codesnippets.joyent.com/posts/show/414)
4. cucumber features/running.feature
5. read the files in features/ to see what's going on